Programming in assembly in Emacs is possible.  See these pages.

* AsmMode -- Assembly mode that comes with Emacs.
* [[Asm86Mode]] -- Asm86 assembly mode.
* GasMode (Lisp:gas-mode.el) -- A more advanced version of asm-mode written from scratch.
* MixalMode -- Programming in MIX assembly.
* PicAsmMode -- Assembly mode for PIC microcontrollers.

----
